&lt;p&gt;Taken from
&lt;a href=&quot;https://plainjs.com/javascript/events/running-code-when-the-document-is-ready-15/&quot; rel=&quot;noreferrer&quot;&gt;https://plainjs.com/javascript/events/running-code-when-the-document-is-ready-15/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

